@startuml state-student-verification
!theme plain
title State machine — Student.verification_status (eDnevnik verifikacija)

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #FEFEFE
  BorderColor #333333
}

[*] --> unverified : student registracija \n(self-service ili admin import)

state unverified {
  unverified : default nakon kreiranja
  unverified : podaci uneseni ručno
}

state pending #FFF5CC {
  pending : VerifyStudentWithEDnevnikJob \ndispatch-ovan u queue
  pending : čeka HTTP response
}

state verified #E0FFE0 {
  verified : podaci match-uju eDnevnik
  verified : može biti član ekipe
}

state mismatched #FFE8D0 {
  mismatched : delta sa eDnevnikom (ime, \ndatum rođenja, škola, ili razred)
  mismatched : admin ručno odlučuje
}

state failed #FFE0E0 {
  failed : eDnevnik nedostupan
  failed : ili 404 (učenik ne postoji)
  failed : ili 401 (API key nevažeći)
}

unverified --> pending : admin pokreće verifikaciju \n(UC8)

pending --> verified : 200 OK + svi podaci match
pending --> mismatched : 200 OK + delta postoji
pending --> failed : 404 Not Found \nili 503 timeout (3× retry) \nili 401 Unauthorized

mismatched --> verified : admin ručno potvrđuje \n(prihvata delta)
mismatched --> unverified : admin reset \n(zahtijeva re-import)

failed --> pending : admin retry \n(nakon što se eDnevnik vrati online)

verified --> pending : re-verifikacija \n(npr. nakon promjene podataka)

note right of pending
  Retry policy (spec §7.4.3):
  - 503: 3× exp backoff (2s, 4s, 8s)
  - 429: čitaj Retry-After header
  - 401: critical, ne retry-uje se
end note

note bottom of failed
  failed nije terminalno —
  admin može retry-ovati kad
  eDnevnik bude dostupan.
end note

@enduml
